name: Girls Crochet Headband - Red Black and White
description:
This Beautiful Head Band is perfect for any little girl. The band is made from elastic so it will stretch to fit babies most head sizes up to the age of 2 or 8.

The Flower has been Crochet from a Beautiful Red Cotton, I have also added a lovely Red Flet Flower with some hand stitching and a Black and White Fabric.

If you have any questions please feel free to contact me. I also love making custom orders so if you would like this but in a different color/size please also feel free to contact me.


Thanks for looking :)
